text: as girls we are all unique difference in so many ways our journey through life is precious we should never take a moment's for granted love and cherish one another hold are girl friends close to our heart we need to be inspired by the word and encouraged by one another callanan enjoy the journey don't rush through life a journey is about focusing on coming to a place of strength in your own personal walk then it can be a gift to others as god intended
from this place of strength we can inspire others speak life and encourage each other showing the world that a life with god is a life well lived
